  <h3 id='LayoutDesign'>Motion Guided Interior Design</h3>
  <p>
      <b>Yutong Liang</b>, <a href='https://shellguo.com/' target='_blank'>Michelle Guo</a> and <a href='https://pei-xu.github.io/' target='_blank'>Pei Xu</a>
  </p>
  <div class="content">
